OL,3,CGerry Adams libel verdict 'a chilling
OL,4,Ceffect' on journalism
OL,6,FGerry Adams winning his libel case
OL,7,Fagainst the BBC is "bound to have a
OL,8,Fchilling effect" on both the
OL,9,Fjournalism and legal sectors, a legal
OL,10,Fcommentator has said.
OL,12,FJoshua Rosenburg, a legal commentator
OL,13,Fwho worked at the BBC for more than 20
OL,14,Fyears, said Mr Adams' success will
OL,15,F"make people think twice about
OL,16,Fdefending cases... It will make people
OL,17,Fthink twice about investigative
OL,18,Fjournalism".
