OL,6,F"Even if they thought that they were
OL,7,Fin the right, but they simply couldn't
OL,8,Fafford to go to court."
OL,10,FHe added: "It will make people ever
OL,11,Fmore careful to ensure that they don't
OL,12,Fsay something that they can't defend
OL,13,Fand justify in court."
OL,15,FOn Thursday, the former leader of Sinn
OL,16,FFein was awarded E100,000 (#84,000) in
OL,17,Fdamages after winning his libel action
OL,18,Fagainst the BBC over allegations made
OL,19,Fin a Spotlight programme and online
OL,20,Farticle.
